    <description>Created By: Neha Aggrawal
Created Date: 17th  Dec 2020
User Story: https://jira.hyundai-autoever.eu/browse/GD-1224
Purpose: This flow will update the field isValid to false on Vehicle Service Package record when the quanity available on all the related vehicle service package items becomes zero.</description>
    <interviewLabel>AS_UpdateIsValid {!$Flow.CurrentDateTime}</interviewLabel>
    <label>AS_UpdateIsValidOnVehicleServicePackage</label>
    <loops>
